"[Human Male]
Balanced abilities allow high adaptability in any environment.
Capable in the use of striking weapons, firearms, and
Techniques, allowing him to adapt to any class."

"[Newman Male]
Heavily adapted towards the handling of photons.
Physically frail, but unmatched by any other race
at the Force class."

"[Cast Male]
Machine-made, machine tough.
Due to artificial nature, has very weak photon sensitivity,
but can achieve unparalleled heights in physical strength."

"[Dewman Male]
A human-based race created from photon research.
They are characterized by a horn on their forehead and a specialization in photon attacks. Inferior to the other races defense-wise, they make up for that shortcoming with excessive attack power."

"[Human Female]
Balanced abilities allow high adaptability in any environment.
Physically tough and capable of utilizing photons,
is rich in versatility and can fit any class."

"[Newman Female]
Heavily adapted towards the handling of photons.
Dainty and frail, but shows great ability at the
Force class."

"[Cast Female]
Machine-made, machine tough.
Shows great potential in both close-range and
firearm-based combat, but is poor at utilizing photons."

"[Dewman Female]
A human-based race created from photon research.
Characterized by a pair of horns on their forehead, they specialize in photon-oriented attacks.
Their defense leaves something to be desired, but they make incredible superior attackers."

"[Hunter]
Close-range fighters.
High HP, Defense, and Melee Attack."

"[Ranger]
Utilizes ranged weapons to fight at mid-range.
High proficiency at all shooting abilities,

"[Force]
Long-ranged combat class focused on casting Techniques.
Powerful and versatile at the use of Techniques,
but can be strengthened by equipping a Teching weapon."

"[Braver]
A class that uses weapons suited towards a
fighting style focused on timing and distance, a balance between short and long range."

"[Bouncer]
A class capable not only of melee combat, but
Technique use as well. Their true worth lies in
supporting many people in combat."

"[Summoner]
A class that can summon a pet and battle at mid-range by issuing it commands. Through the skillful use of a pet raised with various traits, Summoners demonstrate diverse powers allowing them to respond to many situations."
